<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Nimbly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Nimbly,</orth> with light and easy motion: <bibl n="shak. ven 38" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 4.318" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 318</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.285" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 285</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.12" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 12</bibl>. <cit><quote>the air n. and sweetly recommends itself unto our gentle senses,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 1.6.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 6, 2</bibl></cit> (in a manner enlivening the spirits).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>